Vincent Young (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vincent_Young_(actor) 0 Vincent D. Young (born June 4, 1965 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania) is an American actor best known for playing "Noah Hunter" on the TV Series Beverly Hills, 90210. He was on the show from 1997 to 2000. Young has also made guest appearances on CSI: New York, NCIS, and JAG.
